    "ritrue_faq": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the Moroccan Nila Glow Mask?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>The Moroccan Nila Glow Mask is a 15-minute radiance ritual made with authentic Moroccan Nila (indigo powder), Alpha Arbutin, and Niacinamide. It works to remove tan, even out skin tone, and give your skin an instant healthy glow.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this suitable for all skin types?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! The mask is dermatologically tested and formulated to be gentle on all skin types — oily, dry, combination, and sensitive. It's paraben-free and cruelty-free.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will it stain my skin blue?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>No! While the mask has a beautiful blue colour from Moroccan Nila, it washes off completely. You'll be left with glowing, radiant skin — no blue stains.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How soon will I see results?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Most users report visible glow and freshness after just one use! For best results with tan removal and skin tone evening, we recommend using the mask 2-3 times a week for 2-4 weeks.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the key ingredients?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our star ingredients are: <strong>Moroccan Nila<\/strong> (traditional blue powder for brightening), <strong>Alpha Arbutin<\/strong> (fades dark spots), and <strong>Niacinamide<\/strong> (minimizes pores and strengthens skin barrier).<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is COD (Cash on Delivery) available?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! We offer Cash on Delivery across India. Free shipping is available on all prepaid orders.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does one tube last?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>One tube typically lasts 4-6 weeks with regular use (2-3 times per week). Each application requires only a thin, even layer.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I apply the mask?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Step 1: Apply an even layer on clean, dry face (avoid eye area). Step 2: Wait 15 minutes. Step 3: Rinse with lukewarm water and pat dry. Use 2-3 times a week for best results.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_9": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it with other skincare products?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! The mask works well with your existing skincare routine. Apply it on clean skin before your moisturizer and sunscreen. Avoid using it immediately after exfoliating acids.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_10": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I have sensitive skin?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our formula is designed to be gentle and is suitable for sensitive skin. However, we always recommend doing a small patch test on your inner wrist 24 hours before first use.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["faq_1", "faq_2", "faq_3", "faq_4", "faq_5", "faq_6", "faq_7", "faq_8", "faq_9", "faq_10"],
